  "title": "chore(deps): update dependency postcss-scss to v1.0.6",
  "body": "This PR contains the following updates:\n\n| Package | Type | Update | Change | References |\n|---|---|---|---|---|\n| postcss-scss | devDependencies | patch | `1.0.4` -> `1.0.6` | [source](https://renovatebot.com/gh/postcss/postcss-scss) |\n\n---\n\n### Release Notes\n\n<details>\n<summary>postcss/postcss-scss</summary>\n\n### [`v1.0.6`](https://renovatebot.com/gh/postcss/postcss-scss/blob/master/CHANGELOG.md#&#8203;106)\n\n[Compare Source](https://renovatebot.com/gh/postcss/postcss-scss/compare/1.0.5...1.0.6)\n\n-   Fix parsing nested at-rules without semicolon, params, and spaces.\n-   Fix parsing string in interpolation in string.\n\n### [`v1.0.5`](https://renovatebot.com/gh/postcss/postcss-scss/blob/master/CHANGELOG.md#&#8203;105)\n\n[Compare Source](https://renovatebot.com/gh/postcss/postcss-scss/compare/1.0.4...1.0.5)\n\n-   Fix parsing `url( http://example.com )` with spaces inside.\n\n</details>\n\n---\n\n### Renovate configuration\n\n:date: **Schedule**: \"every weekend\" in timezone Europe/Paris.\n\n:vertical_traffic_light: **Automerge**: Enabled.\n\n:recycle: **Rebasing**: Whenever PR is stale, or if you modify the PR title to begin with \"`rebase!`\".\n\n:no_bell: **Ignore**: Close this PR and you won't be reminded about this update again.\n\n---\n\nThis PR has been generated by [Renovate Bot](https://renovatebot.com/gh/marketplace/renovate). View repository job log [here](https://renovatebot.com/dashboard#algolia/instantsearch.js).",
